html(lang='en', xmlns='http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml')
  head
    
    title Messages ( messages)

    include header



  body

    include _nav

    .grid
      .row

        div.desktop-12

          h1.divide-section Progress
          p.info Defines different styles for progress bars.
          h2 Usage
          p
            | The progress bar consists of a background bar and the progress bar itself, indicating the increase.
          table.table
            thead
              tr
                th Class
                th Description
            tbody
              tr
                td
                  code .progress
                td
                  | This class is used on the parent container to create the background of the progress bar.
              tr
                td
                  code .progress-bar
                td
                  | This class needs to be added to the child element to create the actual progress bar.
          
          .preview-box
            .progress
              .progress-bar(style='width: 40%;') 40%
          
  
          hr
          
          h2 Size modifiers
          p
            | Add the 
            code .progress-mini
            |  or 
            code .progress-small
            |  class to change the size of the bar.
          

          
          .preview-box
            .progress.progress-mini
              .progress-bar(style='width: 50%;')
            .progress.progress-small
              .progress-bar(style='width: 55%;')
            .progress
              .progress-bar(style='width: 60%;')
          

          hr
          
          h2 Color modifiers
          p
            | To apply different colors to your progress bars, just add the 
            code .progress-success
            |  , 
            code .progress-warning
            |  or 
            code .progress-danger
            |  class.
          
          .preview-box
            .progress.progress-success
              .progress-bar(style='width: 75%;')
            .progress.progress-warning
              .progress-bar(style='width: 55%;')
            .progress.progress-danger
              .progress-bar(style='width: 35%;')
              
          hr
          
          h3 Striped
          p
            | To create a striped progress bar, use the 
            code .striped
            |  class.
          
         
          .preview-box
            .progress.progress-striped
              .progress-bar(style='width: 65%;')
            
          p
            | You can even animate the striped bar. To do so, just add the 
            code .active
            |  class.
          
         
          .preview-box
            .progress.progress-striped.active
              .progress-bar(style='width: 85%;')
            
          hr
          
          h3 Combinable
          p All modifiers of the Progress component can be combined with each other.
          
          .preview-box
            .progress.progress-small.progress-danger.progress-striped.active
              .progress-bar(style='width: 55%;')
            
